      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"1. CADILLAC LANDAU has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (18.01) at this track in a Other. Safe beginner and drawn well on the inside. Can turn form around here. 8. WARIO was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 2.5 lengths away in second (17.70). Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Will give a great sight again. 7. JUST ALFIE drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.5 lengths from the winner Mister Cadillac in second(22.95) at this track. Form from his last run is proving strong. Expected to be in the finish again. 2. MISTER CADILLAC jumps at a shorter distance and still warrants respect.\",\"runners\":[1,8,7,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
